## Epic D — Git Push, Fetch, Mirror, and Remote Workflows

### Goal

Finish Git remote workflows while keeping Git mutations explicit, auditable, and capability-gated.

### Workstreams

#### D1. Push API

Add:

```http
POST /api/v1/repos/:repo_id/push
```

Request:

```json
{
  "remoteName": "origin",
  "remoteUrl": "https://example.invalid/repo.git",
  "refspecs": ["refs/heads/agent/x:refs/heads/agent/x"],
