# 11. Production Rollout Plan

## Phase 1 — Internal Dev Production-Like

- Connected auth with test JWKS.
- Sandbox backend enabled.
- Storage lock/recovery enabled.
- SDK live tests enabled.
- No external users.

## Phase 2 — Controlled Agent Workloads

- Limited repository set.
- Restricted path grants.
- No Git push except dry-run.
- Read-only and verification exec only.
- Full audit review.

## Phase 3 — Write Workloads

- Workspace write/commit enabled.
- Binary APIs enabled.
- Snapshot/artifact export enabled.
- Push enabled for selected actors/refs.

## Phase 4 — Federation Pilot

- Two or more TreeDB nodes.
- Mirror read policy enabled.
- Federated query enabled for selected repos.
- Leakage test fixtures required in CI.

## Phase 5 — General Production

- SLOs active.
- Incident runbooks complete.
- Backup/restore regularly tested.
- Security checklist complete.
- SDK docs published.

